<h3>New API key</h3>
<p>From this page, you can register a new API key. The key is pre-set for you for security; copy it and add a name for
  the app (or user) that will use it, then click Register.</p>

<%= form_for @key, :url => :admin_new_key do |f| %>
  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :key %><br/>
    <%= f.text_field :key, :value => @key.key, :class => "form-control" %>
  </div><br/>
  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :app_name %><br/>
    <%= f.text_field :app_name, :class => "form-control" %>
  </div><br/>
  <div class="field">
    <%= f.submit "Register", :class => "btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
